The guesthouse that changes your city experience

book-now

    We offer a real low price alternative for your nights in the heart of
   a neighbourhood that has kept its soul, just 15 minutes from main
   tourist attractions, 10 minutes to the Rhone banks and only 2 metro
   stops Perrache and Part-Dieu train and bus stations!
   The Flâneur, first guesthouse to operate as Scop (co-operative), is
   proud to join the players in the social economy, of which the
   neighbourhood is a great ambassador, with a way to look at the economy
   and life in a different manner.
   Discover our great space dedicated to our strollers to share authentic
   life experiences (a common area of 160m2 does offer many
   possibilities!) as well as a passionate team, determined to reveal you
   the best tips of Lyon, the terraces not to be missed, the best local
   merchants and our best discoveries… Hanging around is a real lifestyle,
   ready for the trip?

